{"type": "article", "id": 7097, "title": "“Marenco” 椅子", "description": "\r\n", "date": "2015-03-05T07:29:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">为了庆祝伊势丹内部地板的重新设计，日本当红时装品牌 N.HOOLYWOOD 和意大利现代设计品牌 Arflex 合作共同推出了一款椅子，奶白色布面印满黑色的字，极具现代感。“Marenco” 沙发的创新之处在于这款沙发没有底盘，其坐垫和扶手直接落到地上。你可以</span><a href=\"http://www.classicdesign.it/pouff-marenco_arflex-it.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"white-space:normal;\">点击这里</a><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">购买。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234331EayCZv3IAkJh2N5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052343318nDscNPVfKZevkT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.85535714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<br>\r\n\t</p>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}